Package com.adobe.cq.social.members.api Description

This package contains interfaces for getting information for community users and community groups. The CommunityMemberGroup class provides functionality for getting basic information for community group. The CommunityMemberGroupCollection class provides functionality for getting list of CommunityMemberGroup according to filters. The CommunityMemberGroupProfile class provides functionality for getting profile information for target group. The CommunityMemberUser class provides functionality for getting basic information for community user. The CommunityMemberUserCollection class provides functionality for getting list of CommunityMemberUser according to filters. The CommunityMemberUserProfile class provides functionality for getting profile information for target user. The MembersUtils class provides functionality for getting the CommunityMemberGroupProfile for the specified user id with the specified resource type.
